SQL Lesson 7: Queries with expressions

Synatx, 
SELECT particle_speed / 2.0 AS half_particle_speed
FROM physics_data
WHERE ABS(particle_position) * 10.0 > 500;

1.List all movies and their combined sales in millions of dollars
SELECT title , (domestic_sales+ international_sales)/1000000 AS total_Sales
from movies inner join boxoffice on id = movie_id;

2.List all movies and their ratings in percent
SELECT title , rating*10 AS ALL_RATINGS FROM movies
inner join boxoffice on id = movie_id ;

3.List all movies that were released on even number years
SELECT title , year as Movie_years FROM movies
inner join boxoffice on id = movie_id
where year % 2 == 0;
